plot01 = (
    ggplot(economics)
    + aes(x="date", y="pop")
    + geom_line()
    + labs(x="Data", y="PopulaÃ§Ã£o", title="PopulaÃ§Ã£o ao longo do tempo")
)
plot01.show()
grafico1 = (
    ggplot(mpg)
    + aes(x="class", y="hwy")
    + geom_point()
    + labs(x="Classe", y="Consumo na Estrada (mpg)")
)
grafico1.show()
plot02 = (
    ggplot(mpg)
    + aes(x="class", y="hwy")
    + geom_boxplot()
    + geom_jitter(width=0.2, alpha=0.5)
    + theme_bw()
    + labs(x="Tipo de VeÃ­culo", y="Consumo na Estrada (mpg)")
)
plot02.show()
plot03 = (
    ggplot(mpg)
    + aes(x="class", y="hwy*0.4251")
    + geom_boxplot()
    + geom_jitter(width=0.2, alpha=0.5)
    + theme_bw()
    + labs(
        x="Tipo de VeÃ­culo",
        y="Consumo na Estrada (km/L)",
        title="Consumo de CombustÃ­vel",
        subtitle="VeÃ­culos fabricados entre 1999 e 2008"
    )
)
plot03.show()
grafico2 = (
    ggplot(mpg)
    + aes(x="cyl", y="hwy")
    + geom_point()
    + labs(x="Cilindros", y="Consumo (mpg)")
)
grafico2.show()
plot04 = (
    ggplot(mpg)
    + aes(x="factor(cyl)", y="hwy*0.4251")
    + geom_boxplot()
    + coord_flip()
    + theme_bw()
    + labs(x="NÃºmero de Cilindros", y="Consumo na Estrada (km/L)")
)
plot04.show()
plot05 = (
    ggplot(mpg)
    + aes(x="displ", y="hwy*0.4251")
    + geom_point()
    + facet_grid("year", "class")
    + theme_bw()
    + labs(x="Tamanho do Motor", y="Consumo na Estrada (km/L)")
)
plot05.show()
plot06 = (
    ggplot(mpg)
    + aes(x="displ", y="hwy*0.4251", color="factor(year)")
    + geom_point()
    + facet_grid(cols="class")
    + theme_bw()
    + labs(
        x="Tamanho do Motor",
        y="Consumo na Estrada (km/L)",
        color="Ano de FabricaÃ§Ã£o",
        title="Consumo de CombustÃ­vel em FunÃ§Ã£o do Tamanho do Motor",
        subtitle="Motores maiores consomem mais combustÃ­vel"
    )
)
plot06.show()
plot07 = (
    ggplot(mpg)
    + aes(x="displ", y="hwy*0.4251", color="factor(year)")
    + geom_point()
    + facet_grid(cols="class")
    + theme_bw()
    + labs(
        x="Tamanho do Motor",
        y="Consumo na Estrada (km/L)",
        color="Ano de FabricaÃ§Ã£o",
        title="Consumo de CombustÃ­vel em FunÃ§Ã£o do Tamanho do Motor",
